They say Smaia-sensei can cure
any kind of illness! That's amazing!

rows.label: tlk01000805_msg0002

If I take the teacher's class and
study hard, I wonder if I can
become a doctor too.

Kyukyu-sensei is
so cute, isn't she...

rows.label: tlk01000805_msg0102

An experiment failed
and her fur got a little singed.
I wonder if she's okay...
